results.title: A+X (2012) #5
results.description: A tale of the Immortal Iron Fist and the Indescribable Doop's first adventure!  Plus, what plans are Loki and Mr. Sinister hatching together?

results.title: A+X (2012) #6
results.description: Wolverine and Captain Marvel defend Avengers’ Tower! Plus, Gambit and Thing play the most dangerous game—poker with the Yancy Street Gang.

results.title: A+X (2012) #7
results.description: Thor and Iceman teamup in one of the most visually amazing tales you’ve ever seen.  Plus, the smartest Marvel heroes team-up as Iron Man, Beast and the Hulk do battle…and do science!

results.title: A+X (2012) #8
results.description: Spider-Woman, Kitty Pryde, and Lockheed take on the Absorbing Man! Next up, Hawkeye and Deadpool learn the value of a good trick arrow!

results.title: A+X (2012) #9
results.description: Wolverine teams up with the man who personifies the Avengers - Captain America!  Plus, Wolverine's X-Men students have a spooky team-up with the Sorceror Supreme Doctor Strange.

results.title: A+X (2012) #10
results.description: Black Widow and Fantomex find themselves on opposite sides of the law in Russia! Scarlet Witch and Domino try their luck together!
